# Keep .git — the build derives the OLX version from the git history
# (CMakeOlxVersion.cmake -> get_version_full.sh -> functions.sh).
#
# Exclude in-source CMake build artifacts so a build done on the host can't
# leak into / poison the in-container build (the Dockerfile runs `cmake .`).
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
cmake_install.cmake
bin/
*.o
